---
// Program.astro
---

<section id="program" class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-transparent overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle decorative blob for the section background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-[#B59449]/5 filter blur-[120px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full">
    
    <!-- Title Section -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-[#B59449] uppercase mb-2">
        Program Unggulan
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#063A24] mb-4">
        Jenjang Kelas Tahsin Berjenjang
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-[#063A24]/70 leading-relaxed">
        Pilih tingkatan belajar yang sesuai dengan kemampuan bacaan Anda saat ini. Seluruh kelas dibimbing secara intensif oleh Ustadzah dengan kurikulum terstruktur.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Card Layout Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-[#063A24]/10 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div>
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="bg-[#B59449]/10 text-[#A37F35] text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-max mb-4">
            Tingkat Dasar
          </div>
          <!-- Title -->
          <h3 class="text-[#063A24] text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            Kelas Pra-Tahsin
          </h3>
          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-[#063A24]/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Bimbingan dari dasar (nol) fokus pada perbaikan makhorijul huruf dan pengenalan sifat-sifat huruf hijaiyah secara intensif.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Action Button -->
        <a
          href="#kontak"
          class="w-full text-center bg-[#063A24] text-white font-medium py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#B59449] hover:text-white shadow-sm mt-auto block"
        >
          Pilih Kelas
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-[#063A24]/10 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div>
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="bg-[#B59449]/10 text-[#A37F35] text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-max mb-4">
            Tingkat Menengah
          </div>
          <!-- Title -->
          <h3 class="text-[#063A24] text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            Kelas Tahsin
          </h3>
          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-[#063A24]/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Pendalaman hukum-hukum tajwid (ikhfa, idgham, dll.) serta melancarkan bacaan agar mengalir tartil sesuai kaidah yang benar.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Action Button -->
        <a
          href="#kontak"
          class="w-full text-center bg-[#063A24] text-white font-medium py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#B59449] hover:text-white shadow-sm mt-auto block"
        >
          Pilih Kelas
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-[#063A24]/10 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div>
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="bg-[#B59449]/10 text-[#A37F35] text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-max mb-4">
            Tingkat Lanjutan
          </div>
          <!-- Title -->
          <h3 class="text-[#063A24] text-xl font-bold mb-3">
            Kelas Talaqqi
          </h3>
          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-[#063A24]/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Tingkat lanjutan berupa setoran bacaan Al-Quran secara langsung di hadapan Ustadzah demi meraih akurasi bacaan yang mutqin.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Action Button -->
        <a
          href="#kontak"
          class="w-full text-center bg-[#063A24] text-white font-medium py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#B59449] hover:text-white shadow-sm mt-auto block"
        >
          Pilih Kelas
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
